Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:13.33,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kono sora no kagayaki kimi no mune ni todoiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:13.33,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The luminance of the sky has reached your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:23.36,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}yumemiteta shirabe wa shizukesa no youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:23.36,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The melody I dreamed of was like silence.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.23,0:00:28.41,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no te ga mada yume ni tookutemo
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.23,0:00:28.41,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if your hand is still far away in my dreams,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.25,0:00:33.47,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}omoidashiteyou yasashii koe wo
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.25,0:00:33.47,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I’ll still remember your kind voice
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.23,0:00:46.26,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}dareka ga kimi no tame utatta shiawase no koto
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.23,0:00:46.26,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and the happiness that was sung for you.
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.00,0:00:55.66,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}sora no woto hibike takaku kanashimi wo koete
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.00,0:00:55.66,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Let the sound of the sky ring high over your sadness.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.43,0:01:06.21,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no me ni utsuru mono wa subete hontou no sekai
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.43,0:01:06.21,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything reflected in your eyes is that of the real world.
Dialogue: 6,0:01:06.04,0:01:15.68,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}namida sae kimi wo koko ni todomete okenai
Dialogue: 6,0:01:06.04,0:01:15.68,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even tears won’t be able to stop you here.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.41,0:01:27.81,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}furisosogu hikari no naka ashita wo kanadete
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.41,0:01:27.81,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Amidst the descending lights, you’ll play the song of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly speaking, this snow is a real pain!{Cyber had put snow as show originally. Fruedian much?}{I love how none of you ever change it until it gets to me and make me clean up after you during edit >_<}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially after Command said to pay close attention on patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't given up on Jacott-san, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You search and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you still can't find it, you just have to hope for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I thought you looked a little like Rio-senpai for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath the cliff, at 11 o'clock, about 400 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang in there!{Fix these to something human... er.. english}{HANG THE FUCK IN THERE}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her clothes are frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, take off her coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can switch coats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:19.47,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}A Burning Snow Field
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:19.47,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,75.333333)}{Title}A Visitor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you could actually restore this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the greatest genius in the history of the Academy.{clearly in reference to military academy and her outstanding performance... at age 7}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, our victory is assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Kannagi Noël-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They found her while on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like her left leg is fractured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, her fingers are turning black and red.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frostbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we aren't careful, she'll lose her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.58,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The Helvetian Witch.{German line 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all her fingers as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll stay with her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like she was trying her hardest...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like when she tries to fix Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it.{Cyber had "I see." But given that she knows Noel's past, and is prolly considering it in that light, she's kinda giving a non-commital affirmation of Noel's focus. Perhaps her focus on Take runs deeper, too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could be a spy, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would think they'd meet a Roman soldier in a place like—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've seen a Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls them the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, at first, they'd be more like demons or something...{She IS winner of the anime moron award, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they probably think the same about us in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw her, I thought that Romans...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't seem all that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kanata, you—!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for school lessons to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still disputing at the peace talks, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've heard.{mitai can also be "to hear (a rumor)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you report her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, she'll be taken to Central{command, likely} and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During these uneasy state of affairs{state of affairs, lit}, an enemy has invaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier should be prepared for torture—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How we're going to deal with her is my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me some time, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were carrying her here, did you meet anyone on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I was in a daze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.06,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,A Helvetian soldier...{German line 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you going to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.33,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I? Am I now a Helvetian prisoner{lit.: hostage}?{I think they wanted her to say "prisoner of war", cause it fits much better than hostage -masat}{German Line 3}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.82,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have taken me prisoner—{German line 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:15.68,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Roman Empire's ground forces, 1st Armored Division,{German line 5b}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:24.75,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Armored Battalion, Company B{B Company, choose whatever you want},\NStaff-Sergeant Aisha Aldora{Can't make out the family name- Path suggested Aldora / Aldola, Aldora sounds best to me -N}. ID 1031021.{German line 5}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.55,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Roman Army, Staff-Sergeant Aisha Aldora.{German Line 6}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:37.23,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,ID 1031021.{German Line 7}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Have you learned anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she doesn't understand any Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we've learned is her ID number and that her name is Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the officer in charge of this fort, 2nd Lieutenant Filicia Heideman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have really nice breasts. The kind I really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I rub them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I fondle your whole body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What are you saying all of a sudden, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she really doesn't understand Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't interrogate her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry and find someone who can speak Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can interrogate her and write up a report,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll let her stay with the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for a bit. I thought I'd bet on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens, I'm not a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-chan, welcome to the Time-Trumpeting Fort.{LOL... so I guess we actually used this...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.44,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,"Time-Trum-pet-ing Fort"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Time-Trumpeting Fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:07.28,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So I actually arrived.{German Line 8}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.65,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmother.{German Line 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:56.36,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,To escape, you need strength. That's why I'm going to eat now.{German Line 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she said it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? It's normal for Kanata, but for Noël to be so attached{emotionally}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be... atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:18.05,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Well! Have you ever seen a fossilized angel?{German Line 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Engel"?{KanataGerman}{Vote for leaving it raw like that, since she's not understanding-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:27.46,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, you don't understand a word.{or anything, your decision}{German Line 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have studied Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. If we could just\Nunderstand what she's saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a lot, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yumina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough people to shovel the snow at the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The children are all helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they aren't always little brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People grow everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Kanata-san's bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio would say she still has a ways to go though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Weren't you staying in Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened. It ended up being futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of difficulties there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I heard this horrible rumor about the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.83,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds nice.{German Line 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:35.31,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that these trumpets still exist.{German Line 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.58,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?{German Line 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rio-senpai would have let you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:07.52,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,A nice trumpet. To be able to see something like this—{German Line 16}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya-san's song resounds inside me, and it resounds inside Rio-senpai as well!{we've been using resound, afaik}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the same song isn't just in Helvetia, but it resounds in Rome too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound resounds, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's in Rome or Helvetia, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First-aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.25,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.{German Line 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Danke"?{German for Thank you}{KanataGerman}{She's pronouncing it similar to Thank-You intentionally, I'd wager}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.31,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely, thank you.{German Line 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what "danke" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we were seen after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town hasn't experienced the full effects of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whether it is a parent, a child, or a relative, everyone has lost someone to the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been peaceful, but it'll become miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember Mikhail, the boss of that liquor store?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was at his place until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the Helvetian Army is undergoing a large-scale movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and is heading towards this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's related to that Roman soldier being in this remote place, it's a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, we can't ask her about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san, do you know of anyone who speaks Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know of anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.16,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yumina.{YuminaGerman}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.57,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a servant of the Helvetian Orthodox Church.{I'm a servant of the Helvetian Orthodox Church, choose, edit}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.24,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,May you be blessed a thousandfold with luck.{that's where she says something about Gluck, nonsense to me, used CS subs}{lit.: "I wish you thousandfold luck" - makes no sense to me, too, I guess it's supposed to be a greeting of the Helvetian Orthodox Church -masat}{IMO, it's more related to her trying to relate to the fact that she seems Turkish, with some line similar to "may you be blessed 1000 times over"-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.84,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're just one of those heretics.{German Line 19a}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:33.58,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,There is but one true god. Such a greeting is blasphemy.{German Line 19b}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Just hurry up and ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.24,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?{YuminaGerman}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:49.74,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep quiet, it will be a great bother for everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:56.65,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the least bit thankful, then you should speak openly with us.{lit.: "you should talk honestly."}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:09.04,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to talk about my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:14.13,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I came here is to see the fossilized angel that's supposed to be in this town.{German Line 20}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she came to see the Angel Fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Angel Fossil"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:29.80,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother... in that fortress... she was in that fortress.{German Line 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My grandmother was a soldier at the Time-Trumpeting Fort."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:36.63,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,She was captured at the eastern front and met my grandfather.{German Line 22}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"She was taken prisoner at the eastern battle lines and met my grandfather."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:43.02,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still a child, she often told me about it.{German Line 23}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I grew up listening to her stories."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:52.41,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to see it once at all costs—the angel that my grandmother saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:57.01,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel of the Apocalypse that brought judgement upon the world long ago.{German Line 24}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doctrine is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a demon that came to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. What exactly did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the Angel of the Apocalypse that had destroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A signal to march.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This code is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Royal Guard, 9th Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 9th...? It can't be. Colonel Hopkins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a famous person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's called "The Devil{fierce god} of Vingt{whatever we use}."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he revived weapons from the previous age and wiped out three cities in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you should be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be bad for you if you don't decide what to do fast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hand her over—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Helvetian soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't make it in time did you, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai didn't want anyone else to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she did what she could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why she left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone's together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now give an order as the\Ncommander of the 1121st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, this order is my own judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am taking full responsibility for any consequences of this order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the commander of the 1121st Platoon, 2nd Lieutenant Filicia Heideman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days ago, a Roman spy was captured in Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there was an accident before we could interrogate, so we couldn't confirm anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By coincidence, we received information that a Roman soldier was seen in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! The 1121st's fort is now under the command of my 9th Independent Mobile Division!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout like that all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-san was telling me about the legend of the Flame Maidens, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. She says that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a thorough search!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search every corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover the exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she hasn't asked for your name yet, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.39,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Noël.{YuminaGerman}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:30.56,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.63,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:33.38,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:37.17,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,She is... the Invisible Reaper?{Niphty said that that term was referenced earlier in the series, please look it up}{lit.: You have the invisible demon/devil?}{German Line 25}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Invisible Reaper"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 1121st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large Roman army has appeared on the border of Seize and Nomansland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:46.42,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let’s remember our love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:46.42,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou omoikasanete
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.28,0:22:49.63,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}and play out their importance.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.28,0:22:49.63,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}taisetsu wo kanadeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.55,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}We were so happy that we cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.55,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}ureshikute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:13.55,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}It hurt so much that we laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:13.55,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}itakute waratta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:22.75,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}But these are all proof that we are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:22.75,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}dakedo sonna zenbu ga ikiteru akashi nan desu
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.06,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let’s move forward one step at a time.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.46,0:23:27.06,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}yukkuri aruite yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.52,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:33.03,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let me hear the words of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:33.03,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}hitosashi no honne kikasete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:34.23,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}You’re just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.93,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Even if our love and friendship sometimes waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:39.93,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou toki ni yuretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:40.23,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}I know you know we’ll be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:45.85,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}let’s make it echo forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:45.85,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}zutto zutto hibiki aitai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:46.21,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you count my precious hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.94,0:23:52.19,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:45.94,0:23:52.19,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}arifureteru kotoba de wa tsutaekirenai
Dialogue: 1,0:23:51.90,0:23:57.99,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:51.90,0:23:57.99,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}watashitachi no harmony
Dialogue: 2,0:23:57.89,0:24:03.02,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear it? Our harmony!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:57.89,0:24:03.02,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}kikoeru our harmony
